{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-page-js","path":"/2019/05-18/let-your-static-page-support-https","result":{"data":{"prevPost":{"id":"9ee666ff-e2fb-51c0-9c9b-d9ca8c073fac","fields":{"slug":"/2019/04-09/iview-usage-experience"},"excerpt":"最近开始接触 vue 和 iview。这次将最近使用的经验总结给大家，希望对刚接触 iview 的开发者有一定的帮助。 什么是 iview iview 是基于 vue 开发的主题框架。其设计理念来源于 Ant Design。可以算是 Vue 中的 Ant Design…","timeToRead":11,"frontmatter":{"title":"iview 使用经验总结","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":2.4,"src":"/static/35b03247c4e6d2deedc07b3bf2297ad9/57599/cover.png","srcSet":"/static/35b03247c4e6d2deedc07b3bf2297ad9/c0acf/cover.png 300w,\n/static/35b03247c4e6d2deedc07b3bf2297ad9/5c50c/cover.png 600w,\n/static/35b03247c4e6d2deedc07b3bf2297ad9/57599/cover.png 1200w,\n/static/35b03247c4e6d2deedc07b3bf2297ad9/0035e/cover.png 1800w,\n/static/35b03247c4e6d2deedc07b3bf2297ad9/09c94/cover.png 2400w,\n/static/35b03247c4e6d2deedc07b3bf2297ad9/cffab/cover.png 2870w","sizes":"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"}}},"date":"Apr 9","author":{"id":"blackcater","nickname":"blackcater","avatar":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/3e72cc359750952f52e27f3b2a59a0ff/c0e17/blackcater.png"}}}}}},"nextPost":null,"post":{"id":"01380e1e-cc50-58c0-83d0-a00b1e92b380","fields":{"slug":"/2019/05-18/let-your-static-page-support-https"},"html":"<h2 id=\"什么是静态页面？\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AF%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%9F\" aria-label=\"什么是静态页面？ permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>什么是静态页面？</h2>\n<p>在开始正文之前，为了让所有人都能看懂本篇文章，我先讲解一些很基础的知识。如果你对这些都已知晓，请直接看 <a href=\"#cloudfire\">CloudFire</a> 一节。</p>\n<p>静态页面就是没有数据库交互，对每个人显示的内容一样的页面。我们按设计稿撸出来的页面都是静态页面，只要将这些页面放在机器上，暴露一个地址，就可以访问到。</p>\n<h2 id=\"将静态页面放在-github-上\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B0%86%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8-github-%E4%B8%8A\" aria-label=\"将静态页面放在 github 上 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>将静态页面放在 Github 上</h2>\n<p>Github 允许你存放静态页面，从而让其他人看到。但是如果你有自己的服务器，你的静态页面也是可以变成动态的。Github 只是提供资源文件的托管，如果你的 JS 文件和远程服务器进行交互，这些 Github 都是不予限制的。</p>\n<p>在 Github 上创建的任何一个项目，默认有一个 <code class=\"language-text\">master</code> 分支。Github 可以为每一个项目生成一个访问的地址，基本格式为: <code class=\"language-text\">[项目名].[用户名].github.io</code>。</p>\n<p>默认情况下，你将文件上传到项目的 <code class=\"language-text\">gh-pages</code> 分支即可。很多项目都是这么做的。但是 Github 也支持其他的方式：</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.7244094488189%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Github 对 Github Pages 进行配置\"\n        title=\"Github 对 Github Pages 进行配置\"\n        src=\"/static/7fd3d77a8ca2f4476c9b813b7d4b3adb/f0628/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7fd3d77a8ca2f4476c9b813b7d4b3adb/8c2ab/1.png 300w,\n/static/7fd3d77a8ca2f4476c9b813b7d4b3adb/3f01f/1.png 600w,\n/static/7fd3d77a8ca2f4476c9b813b7d4b3adb/f0628/1.png 1200w,\n/static/7fd3d77a8ca2f4476c9b813b7d4b3adb/59b02/1.png 1524w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Github 对 Github Pages 进行配置</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>前往项目的<strong>设置</strong>目录下，你会看到有一个 <code class=\"language-text\">source</code> 选项：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">master branch</code>: 将 master 分支作为静态页面存放分支。</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">master branch /docs folder</code>: 将 master 分支下的 <code class=\"language-text\">/docs</code> 目录作为静态页面存放分支。</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">None</code>: 默认选项，将 <code class=\"language-text\">gh-pages</code> 分支作为静态页面存放分支。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>对于个人博客，推荐创建一个项目：<code class=\"language-text\">[用户名].github.io</code>。并将静态页面传入该项目的 <code class=\"language-text\">master</code> 分支上。之后访问 <code class=\"language-text\">[用户名].github.io</code> 就能访问到页面了。</p>\n<p><em>注: 静态页面上传完之后，并不是立即就能访问的，因为中间有 CDN 同步之内的一些操作，有一定的延迟，等一会就行了。</em></p>\n<h2 id=\"开发静态页面的技术选型\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E9%80%89%E5%9E%8B\" aria-label=\"开发静态页面的技术选型 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>开发静态页面的技术选型</h2>\n<p>Github 上有很多静态化技术，如:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>早期很出名的 <a href=\"https://github.com/jekyll/jekyll\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">jekyll</a>。</li>\n<li>后来 Node 流行，出现了 <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">hexo</a>。</li>\n<li>Go 语言写的 <a href=\"https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">hugo</a>。</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/react\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">React</a> / <a href=\"https://github.com/vuejs/vue\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Vue</a> / <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Angular</a> 等前端框架书写的网站。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>在最后一条中，我已经将 <a href=\"https://github.com/nozzle/react-static\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">react-static</a>，<a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">gatsby</a>，<a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/Docusaurus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Docusaurus</a> 以及 <a href=\"https://github.com/vuejs/vuepress\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">vuepress</a> 包含进去了 😄。</p>\n<p>甚至，你可以不选上面任何技术方案，直接手写。不过为了效率着想，还是选择成熟的方案为好。</p>\n<h2 id=\"修改访问域名\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D\" aria-label=\"修改访问域名 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>修改访问域名</h2>\n<p>现在我们的静态页面已经可以访问了，但是呢访问地址肯定让很多人都不爽。不过没关系，Github 支持你修改域名。</p>\n<h3 id=\"购买域名\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D\" aria-label=\"购买域名 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>购买域名</h3>\n<p>为了改域名，那得先买个域名。买域名可以去<a href=\"https://cn.aliyun.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">阿里云</a>，<a href=\"https://www.west.cn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">西部数码</a>以及国外的<a href=\"https://sg.godaddy.com/zh/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Godaddy</a>等等。</p>\n<p>买域名的过程我就不说了，和购物一样没啥区别。买的时候需要小心点，别被默认选项坑了就行（默认会勾选一些增值服务等）。</p>\n<p>很多域名可能会做活动，首年很便宜，有的域名可能还免费，不过找一个自己满意的域名肯定十分的蛋疼，大家要有耐心啊。</p>\n<h3 id=\"a，cname-和-mx-记录\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#a%EF%BC%8Ccname-%E5%92%8C-mx-%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95\" aria-label=\"a，cname 和 mx 记录 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>A，CNAME 和 MX 记录</h3>\n<p>我们都知道，当我们输入一个网站例如：<code class=\"language-text\">http://www.qq.com/</code> 为何能到达腾讯的门户网站？为何输入别的就不行？这个就是在你访问的 DNS 机器上有这么一条记录。这条记录就像网址的身份证一样，身份证如果没了，那么你这个人相当于也没了。全球有 13 台跟根服务器，在上面可以找到你的这条记录的。其他遍布全球的 DNS 服务器，都是同步于跟服务器的。</p>\n<p>A 记录用来指定域名对应的 IP 地址的。通俗来说就是告诉 DNS，当你输入域名的时候给你引导到对应的服务器。</p>\n<p>CNAME 记录也叫别名记录，允许你将多个名字映射到同一台计算机。</p>\n<p>MX 记录也叫邮件路由记录，用户可以将该域名下的邮件服务器指向自己的邮件服务器上。</p>\n<h3 id=\"修改记录\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95\" aria-label=\"修改记录 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>修改记录</h3>\n<p>各个域名服务商的控制台都各不相同，但大同小异。这里我以 <a href=\"https://www.west.cn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">西部数码</a> 的为例（因为我的域名是在西部数码买的 😭）。</p>\n<p>在 “域名管理” 目录下，找到 “域名解析” 服务。</p>\n<p>我们添加一条 CNAME 记录：将 <code class=\"language-text\">www.[域名]</code> 映射到 <code class=\"language-text\">[网站].github.io</code> 地址上。</p>\n<p>之后我们在静态项目更目录下补上一个 <code class=\"language-text\">CNAME</code> 文件，<code class=\"language-text\">CNAME</code> 文件内写上：<code class=\"language-text\">www.[域名]</code>。</p>\n<p>提交代码之后等待一会儿即可。</p>\n<h2 id=\"cloudfire\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cloudfire\" aria-label=\"cloudfire permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CloudFire</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cloudflare.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">CloundFire</a> 是国外 DNS 服务提供商。我们需要靠他才能让我们的页面支持 HTTPS。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>首先，我们创建一个账号。<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.61911454673226%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Create an account for CloudFire\"\n        title=\"Create an account for CloudFire\"\n        src=\"/static/b88b0dbf28e85bd1bbb6baf99c3df3ee/f0628/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b88b0dbf28e85bd1bbb6baf99c3df3ee/8c2ab/2.png 300w,\n/static/b88b0dbf28e85bd1bbb6baf99c3df3ee/3f01f/2.png 600w,\n/static/b88b0dbf28e85bd1bbb6baf99c3df3ee/f0628/2.png 1200w,\n/static/b88b0dbf28e85bd1bbb6baf99c3df3ee/57025/2.png 1800w,\n/static/b88b0dbf28e85bd1bbb6baf99c3df3ee/8252b/2.png 2400w,\n/static/b88b0dbf28e85bd1bbb6baf99c3df3ee/02e13/2.png 2846w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Create an account for CloudFire</figcaption>\n  </figure></li>\n<li>创建一个项目，这里填写自己购买的域名。<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.196092114445214%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Create a project\"\n        title=\"Create a project\"\n        src=\"/static/717aee42c233aeee7bd1c7b92db9db48/f0628/3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/717aee42c233aeee7bd1c7b92db9db48/8c2ab/3.png 300w,\n/static/717aee42c233aeee7bd1c7b92db9db48/3f01f/3.png 600w,\n/static/717aee42c233aeee7bd1c7b92db9db48/f0628/3.png 1200w,\n/static/717aee42c233aeee7bd1c7b92db9db48/57025/3.png 1800w,\n/static/717aee42c233aeee7bd1c7b92db9db48/8252b/3.png 2400w,\n/static/717aee42c233aeee7bd1c7b92db9db48/a2a05/3.png 2866w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Create a project</figcaption>\n  </figure></li>\n<li>创建之后会进行 DNS 查询，可能会查询失败，失败之后需要我们手动添加一下。<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.28172942817294%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Search DNS\"\n        title=\"Search DNS\"\n        src=\"/static/64afdc410d652830ff63221f58ca6f6c/f0628/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/64afdc410d652830ff63221f58ca6f6c/8c2ab/4.png 300w,\n/static/64afdc410d652830ff63221f58ca6f6c/3f01f/4.png 600w,\n/static/64afdc410d652830ff63221f58ca6f6c/f0628/4.png 1200w,\n/static/64afdc410d652830ff63221f58ca6f6c/57025/4.png 1800w,\n/static/64afdc410d652830ff63221f58ca6f6c/8252b/4.png 2400w,\n/static/64afdc410d652830ff63221f58ca6f6c/cfe4d/4.png 2868w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Search DNS</figcaption>\n  </figure></li>\n<li>之后我们获取到了两个 DNS 地址 <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.17470300489168%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Get two DNS address\"\n        title=\"Get two DNS address\"\n        src=\"/static/6035695a8a76cebf340f068081567e92/f0628/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6035695a8a76cebf340f068081567e92/8c2ab/5.png 300w,\n/static/6035695a8a76cebf340f068081567e92/3f01f/5.png 600w,\n/static/6035695a8a76cebf340f068081567e92/f0628/5.png 1200w,\n/static/6035695a8a76cebf340f068081567e92/57025/5.png 1800w,\n/static/6035695a8a76cebf340f068081567e92/8252b/5.png 2400w,\n/static/6035695a8a76cebf340f068081567e92/22847/5.png 2862w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Get two DNS address</figcaption>\n  </figure></li>\n<li>由于我的域名在 西部数码 购买的，所以这里我以西部数码为例对 DNS 服务器进行修改 <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.622905027932966%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Change DNS Server\"\n        title=\"Change DNS Server\"\n        src=\"/static/c6c0367aeb39cc5f8dbf57db0293d971/f0628/6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c6c0367aeb39cc5f8dbf57db0293d971/8c2ab/6.png 300w,\n/static/c6c0367aeb39cc5f8dbf57db0293d971/3f01f/6.png 600w,\n/static/c6c0367aeb39cc5f8dbf57db0293d971/f0628/6.png 1200w,\n/static/c6c0367aeb39cc5f8dbf57db0293d971/57025/6.png 1800w,\n/static/c6c0367aeb39cc5f8dbf57db0293d971/8252b/6.png 2400w,\n/static/c6c0367aeb39cc5f8dbf57db0293d971/126fe/6.png 2864w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Change DNS Server</figcaption>\n  </figure></li>\n<li>点击下一步之后，我们就等待几个小时就行了（可能几分钟就行了）。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>现在，我们地址以 <code class=\"language-text\">https</code> 开头进行访问，是不是已经可以看到自己的网站了？Cool！</p>\n<h2 id=\"强制-https-访问\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%BC%BA%E5%88%B6-https-%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE\" aria-label=\"强制 https 访问 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>强制 HTTPS 访问</h2>\n<p>虽然我们的网站可以 <code class=\"language-text\">https</code> 进行访问，但是我们 <code class=\"language-text\">http</code> 也能进行访问。这里我们需要去 Github 上设置一下：</p>\n<p>在项目的设置页面下，我们可以找到一个 <code class=\"language-text\">Enforce HTTPS</code> 选项，我们勾选上它，等待一会~</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 77.19950433705081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Enforce HTTPS\"\n        title=\"Enforce HTTPS\"\n        src=\"/static/0b6ce35027584e0fedc658a6e24aa660/f0628/7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0b6ce35027584e0fedc658a6e24aa660/8c2ab/7.png 300w,\n/static/0b6ce35027584e0fedc658a6e24aa660/3f01f/7.png 600w,\n/static/0b6ce35027584e0fedc658a6e24aa660/f0628/7.png 1200w,\n/static/0b6ce35027584e0fedc658a6e24aa660/191cb/7.png 1614w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Enforce HTTPS</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>现在访问 <code class=\"language-text\">http</code> 地址试试？是不是立即就跳转到 <code class=\"language-text\">https</code> 去了？</p>\n<p>最终效果就像<a href=\"https://www.blackcater.win\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">我的博客</a>效果一样。</p>","excerpt":"什么是静态页面？ 在开始正文之前，为了让所有人都能看懂本篇文章，我先讲解一些很基础的知识。如果你对这些都已知晓，请直接看 CloudFire…","headings":[{"value":"什么是静态页面？","depth":2},{"value":"将静态页面放在 Github 上","depth":2},{"value":"开发静态页面的技术选型","depth":2},{"value":"修改访问域名","depth":2},{"value":"购买域名","depth":3},{"value":"A，CNAME 和 MX 记录","depth":3},{"value":"修改记录","depth":3},{"value":"CloudFire","depth":2},{"value":"强制 HTTPS 访问","depth":2}],"timeToRead":8,"wordCount":{"paragraphs":54,"sentences":54,"words":260},"frontmatter":{"title":"让你的静态页面支持 https","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":2.4,"src":"/static/2723250560fbecbb676b5db28997150f/57599/cover.png","srcSet":"/static/2723250560fbecbb676b5db28997150f/c0acf/cover.png 300w,\n/static/2723250560fbecbb676b5db28997150f/5c50c/cover.png 600w,\n/static/2723250560fbecbb676b5db28997150f/57599/cover.png 1200w,\n/static/2723250560fbecbb676b5db28997150f/cea64/cover.png 1520w","sizes":"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"}}},"date":"May 18","author":{"id":"blackcater","nickname":"blackcater","avatar":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/3e72cc359750952f52e27f3b2a59a0ff/c0e17/blackcater.png"}}}},"tags":null,"series":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"01380e1e-cc50-58c0-83d0-a00b1e92b380","prevSlug":"/2019/04-09/iview-usage-experience","nextSlug":""}}}